15bc9041c1f8e4c606257b1b539192cb4dbdd94d6e8c08722151f7a20f62040bbc900251fa334da79c4cee8c5cdddeb1423d671e06c0712f31bd1d2917ba37cc  0001-Specify-soname-instead-of-linker-name-for-dynamic-li.patch
